I"õ)<img src="/assets/Differ/Automate1Header.png" alt="Which is it">
<div class="image-caption">This is a simple automation fade of a test signal in a DAW... which is it?</div>

<p><a href="/music/2019/02/17/Daw-V-Daw-Differ.html">Last time I set out to show that DAWs are different in common use</a>, and folks were curious about the automation part.</p>

<p>So let‚Äôs dive deeper and let me show you how to replicate (or refute!) my tests.</p>

