<h1 id="conclusion">Conclusion</h1>

<p><strong>DO NOT TRUST ME</strong>. Try this yourself. <a href="https://sonicvisualiser.org">The tools are free</a>.</p>

<p>Should you care? Probably not. Is it interesting? I hope so.</p>

<p>Should you drop your favorite software over this? Very unlikely.</p>

<p>Some companies have some real issues though.</p>

